description:
This course will get you on the road to studying effectively for the TOEFL listening section. You will learn proven strategies for each question as well as the structure of the section. It's important to study in a way that will give you unlimited upside and at the same time avoid the enemy of all test takers, frustration.

This course should take about an hour to complete. However, I would recommend that you review the videos every once in awhile to make sure your on the right track. After the videos are completed you can take a section of a test and see the notes I took when I heard the audio.
title: TOEFL ibt Listening -getting to 80
